values:
I just woke up, still exhausted and rather hungry. Kind of lonely too.

I'm really not sure what's going on anymore.&nbsp;I honselty thought I knew everything I had to know, everything there was to know, but I was wrong. I experienced something I never felt before, but I'm not sure that's what I really needed...it's just fucking me up now.

While I laid in bed earlier, I had a lot to say,&nbsp;more than I probably should, but now&nbsp;I just don't have the energy to get into it all. I'm thinking a walk would do me good. i need to leave this&nbsp;house...the&nbsp;room.&nbsp;

Come find me if you want to see me. I'll be back...eventually.&nbsp;
